    <h1>Managing currencies</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you want to offer your items for sale in different countries, working with various currencies is essential. This page describes the necessary settings you have to carry out in your plentymarkets system for this purpose.</p>
