<h2 id="20">2. Converting currencies</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <a href="/en/item/settings/prices">Setup » Item » Sales prices</a> and activate the option <strong>Currency: Live conversion</strong> to determine if the currency conversion in the online shop is carried out automatically.<br>
In addition, carry out general currency settings for all incoming orders in the menu <strong>Setup » Orders » Payment » Currencies</strong>. To do so, proceed as described below.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Converting currencies:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Orders » Payment » Currencies</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings according to <a href="#table-settings-currencies">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
