<div class="title">System currency vs. Online shop currency</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This setting is not necessarily identical to the currency displayed in your online shop. You can define a different standard currency for each online shop and each language. Further information on these settings are provided on the manual page <a href="/en/online-store/setting/setting-up-ceres#201">Carrying out currency settings</a>. This page deals directly with setting up your plentyShop.</p>
</div>
